{"tid":1739051,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我系撑警，我有野想講","createTime":"2019-11-19T12:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T12:50:20.000Z","uid":301384,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"464100af5344bf61fe9eeda28348610cc29820f2","tid":1739051,"uid":301384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:40:46.000Z","msg":"其實我地衣家踩左落陣地戰陷阱，<br />\n我明有d地方，例如自己學校，<br />\n大家都好想守護，但系要其實<br />\n守嘅成本超高，自己那野，<br />\n救你嘅手足都那野，<br />\n所以<br />\n總結經驗，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔玩陣地戰</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">回歸be water 嘅奮鬥目標</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>記得有次開花一成功</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n系瘋狂遊擊，不斷轉陣地，<br />\n<br />\n避免困守，被包圍，跟住又有手足被捕</span></strong></span><br />\n我知講呢d可能被人屌，但忠言逆耳:<br />\n即系咁，<br />\n唔好成日怪<span style=\"font-size: large;\">散水撚</span>，<br />\n有時死守，系真系害死自己手足，<br />\n<br />\n衣家警察系<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無人性</span></strong></strong></span>拿真槍，開車撞人，<br />\n<br />\n全部人推埋，死硬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以光明正大鬥，會好傷，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">要玩喑嘅</span></span><br />\n其<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>都做得，<br />\n用<span style=\"color: red;\">網絡公sum</span>，瘋傳照片群插佢地，一人一插，<br />\n但系記得用VPN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果成功<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阻止</span></span><br />\n到狗仔女(除非黄絲)自殺，<br />\n系勝利一種<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">例如帶圖post句，&quot;我支持你冇撚去自殺啊，臭西&quot; cap 圖 彼第二個再輔句</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然好膠，但願<span style=\"color: red;\">抛磚引玉</span>，<br />\n希望大家提多d暗招，<br />\n最重要將<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暗招普及化，諗計降低風險，因為暗招人多先有用</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6db64fd682076cef7eb46b40dad6ebad0a4e9f","tid":1739051,"uid":84355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:45:27.000Z","msg":"根本玩陣地一定輸，黑狗瘋狂補給，set rd block封我地補給同人手邊有得打"},{"pid":"c60968431b442ee733923a71877265fa883c22e4","tid":1739051,"uid":122930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:50:20.000Z","msg":"一擊即閃， 融入於市<br />\n記住車同屋企先係春袋"}]}